<h4 style="font-weight: normal">A short explanation: A vpn stands for Virtual Private Network. If a website or file trys to log your ip and send it
to a hacker your network could be at risk. A VPN allows you too mask your IP. Due too this if a hacker tried to
"DDOS" you your network would be shutdown unless you use a VPN! If you need more info go here: 
</h4><a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/133680/htg-explains-what-is-a-vpn/">Click me to learn more!</a>
